10. Easy navigation = good UX
11. The UI must be in blue and green colour 
12. The user must get an option to change it to dark or light mode
	if light mode -- use black, light blue colour and light green colour
	else use white, dark blue colour and dark green colour
13. if dark mode selected, text must be in white colour
	else the text must be in black colour
14. Keep the buttons bold



